---
---
<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="services-header">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Full-Service<br/>Electrical Work</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub">
      From panel upgrades to full commercial builds — we handle every phase of the electrical scope with a crew that shows up prepared and finishes clean.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">Residential Electrical</div>
      <p class="service-desc">New installs, rewires, outlet upgrades, ceiling fans, smoke detectors, and everything in between. Done right the first time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">Commercial &amp; Office</div>
      <p class="service-desc">Retail fit-outs, office build-outs, lighting systems, and data/power infrastructure for businesses across the region.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">Panel Upgrades</div>
      <p class="service-desc">200A service upgrades, subpanel installs, load center replacements — safe, code-compliant, and inspected.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="7" y1="12" x2="17" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="7" x2="12" y2="17"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">New Construction</div>
      <p class="service-desc">Rough-in, trim-out, and final for custom homes and commercial builds. We coordinate with GCs and pass every inspection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 010 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 000 14.14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">EV Charger Install</div>
      <p class="service-desc">Level 2 home and commercial EV charging station installation. Permits pulled, panels verified, chargers activated.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">Lighting &amp; Fixtures</div>
      <p class="service-desc">Recessed lighting, LED retrofits, outdoor security lights, under-cabinet lighting — any scope, any style.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card fade-up">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="16"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="14" y2="14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="service-title">Generator Install</div>
      <p class="service-desc">Whole-home standby generator installation — automatic transfer switches, proper grounding, permit coordination with your utility.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
